description: This file is the entry point for a React web application. It imports React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component, then renders the App component within a root element identified by 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering a React application into the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the root DOM element.
